1. nginx配置文件默认在 /usr/local/etc/nginx/nginx.conf
2. nginx -t 
nginx会去测试你得配置文件得语法，并告诉你配置文件是否写得正确，同时也告诉了你配置文件得路径

安装nginx:
https://juejin.cn/post/6986190222241464350

Brew装好nginx后查看常用命令
https://blog.csdn.net/sun124608666/article/details/123384122

启动nginx
brew services start nginx

关闭nginx
brew services stop nginx

热更新nginx
nginx -s reload

使用homebrew安装nginx
Brew install nginx

查看nginx配置信息
brew info nginx